sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant A as Go 接入服务
    participant R as Redis
    participant M as RocketMQ
    participant S as Reservation 扫描器
    participant O as 订单消费者
    participant P as PostgreSQL

    A->>R: Lua 预占成功
    R-->>A: PENDING_MESSAGE
    Note over A: 进程在发送 MQ 前宕机

    S->>R: 获取到期的 PENDING_MESSAGE
    R-->>S: reservation + 固定 message_id

    S->>M: 补发同一 message_id
    M-->>S: ACK

    M->>O: 投递消息
    O->>P: Inbox + Token + Order + Outbox
    P-->>O: COMMIT
    O-->>M: ACK
